Q17.Add or append in paragraph text and also in the numbered(ordered) 
    list in a given HTML document using jQuery selectors. 
i. [Hint: Use Append() method] 

Answer::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
<html>
<head>
	<script src="jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
	<script>
	$(document).ready(function()
	{
		$("p").append("Hello");
			$("ol").append("<li>Mango</li>");
	});
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<p>This is paragraph </p>
	<ol type="1">
	<li>Apple</li>
	</ol>
</body>
</html>
